data.description: This inviting home boasts three spacious bedrooms and two modern bathrooms, making it an ideal choice for comfortable living. Inside, the open floor plan seamlessly connects the living room and dining room, creating a welcoming and versatile living space for family and friends.  The master bedroom comes complete with an ensuite bathroom, providing a private retreat within the home. Situated on a generous lot, the property includes an attached two-car garage and offers plenty of outdoor space for various activities and gardening. Located in the charming Olivehurst/Linda area, this home has been thoughtfully upgraded and remodeled, featuring luxurious vinyl flooring, new baseboards, a freshly fenced backyard, updated bathrooms, electrical enhancements, new appliances, a fully remodeled kitchen with a new pantry and added bar, and convenient access to nearby freeways, making it the perfect opportunity for first-time homebuyers.
